Big thanks to Gabi who was able to take over my training while I was sick :) Hope you guys enjoyed the sequence I prepared.

General warm-up

  • 5 minutes run

Round 1

  • Jumping Jacks
  • Bicycle crunches

Round 2

  • Mountain climbers
  • Side plank with leg raise

Round 3

  • Prisoner squad with jump
  • Narrow push ups

Round 4

  • Jumping lunges
  • Superman

Round 5

  • Squad with front kick
  • High plank shoulder taps

Round 6

  • Bench kicks
  • Star crunches

Round 7

  • Jumping plank
  • Reverse triceps

Round 8

  • High knees
  • Side crunch

Bonus

  • 15 burpies
  • Punching abs

Cool down

  • General stretching

Sketch :)
